A warm, sunlit living room scene in Studio Ghibli style featuring two identical teenage boys with messy hair sitting on a cozy couch, looking slightly embarrassed while their father sits in an armchair nearby with an exaggeratedly protective yet playful expression, arms crossed and eyebrow raised. Through a large window, a vintage sports car is visible pulling into the driveway. The room is filled with whimsical details: family photos on the walls, a cat stretching on the floor, and warm golden afternoon light streaming through sheer curtains. The color palette is soft pastels with rich amber tones, capturing a humorous yet tender family moment with expressive animated faces and gentle brushstroke textures characteristic of Japanese animation.
